        },
        {
          "body": "Suyin Beifong",
          "key": "${link_2}",
          "target": {
            "href": "Suyin_Beifong",
            "page": "Suyin_Beifong"
          }
        },
        {
          "body": "metalbender",
          "key": "${link_3}",
          "target": {
            "href": "Metalbending",
            "page": "Metalbending"
          }
        }
      ],
      "text": "Three years later, Izumi traveled to Republic City in her official capacity as Fire Lord to attend Prince Wu's coronation as the 54th Earth King. There, she sat next to her father and witnessed Kuvira denounce Wu's authority and dissolve the Earth Kingdom in favor of the Earth Empire under her own rule. Izumi and the other world leaders convened after the coronation and agreed to send Suyin Beifong as their representative to speak with Kuvira and convince the metalbender to step down."
    },
    {
      "body": "Weeks after Korra failed to stop Kuvira from ${link_0} ${link_1}, Izumi attended a meeting of the world leaders, although without the ${link_2}' representatives, at ${link_3}. She was unimpressed with Wu's suggestion to attack Kuvira with an army of \"highly trained ${link_4}\", and her glare toned down the eccentric ideas of the Earth Kingdom royal. Before they could continue, their meeting was interrupted by ${link_5} and ${link_6} and later by ${link_7} and ${link_8}, who all alerted them of Kuvira's plan to manufacture a ${link_9}.",
