        }
      ],
      "text": "Weeks after Korra failed to stop Kuvira from taking Zaofu, Izumi attended a meeting of the world leaders, although without the Water Tribes' representatives, at City Hall. She was unimpressed with Wu's suggestion to attack Kuvira with an army of \"highly trained badgermoles\", and her glare toned down the eccentric ideas of the Earth Kingdom royal. Before they could continue, their meeting was interrupted by Korra and Opal and later by Bolin and Varrick, who all alerted them of Kuvira's plan to manufacture a spirit vine-powered super weapon."
    },
    {
      "body": "Izumi refused to support a preemptive strike against ${link_0} during a meeting with the other ${link_1} leaders at ${link_2}.",
      "links": [
        {
          "body": "Kuvira",
          "key": "${link_0}",
